<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I was testing generated atom feeds with Zend_Test and I noticed that when the xml prolog (&lt;?xml ... ?&gt;) is included, like in every Zend_Feed, the query fails. The fault is of the underlying DOMDocument class, but I think the prolog can be stripped before creating the DOMDocument.</p>

